    "This aggregated tensor of size 1 × D is forwarded to the FC layers for predicting protein functions.",
    "The present PhiGnet allows us to directly learn information from a sequence alone (without using any structural knowledge) to significantly explore functional sites at the residue level.",
    "To achieve an optimized model, we have to tune and choose values of the hyperparameters in our method, e.g., thresholds for filtering EVCs/RCs (Supplementary Fig.",
